title: I Hatched A Fish From Supermarket Caviar
description: In this video, Max Fosh buys caviar from a supermarket and attempts to hatch fish from the eggs.
summary: Max Fosh buys caviar from a supermarket and tries to hatch fish, resulting in a hilariously absurd experiment.
payoff: The payoff comes when Max actually manages to hatch a fish from the supermarket caviar, showcasing the unexpected and ridiculous outcome of his experiment.
